text: First Blood is a compilation album by the Danish industrial band Psychopomps. It features some of the band's best work as well as earlier recorded version of some songs. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== *Jesper Schmidt: Vox, Programming, Keyboards *Flemming Norre Larsen: Programming, Lyrics ==External links== * Psychopomps at myspace Category:Psychopomps (band) albums Category:1996 compilation albums Category:Zoth Ommog Records compilation albums Category:Cleopatra Records compilation albums
title: First Blood (Psychopomps album)
